text: Nj in all letter case forms NJ Nj nj Nj (all uppercase: NJ, all lowercase: nj) is a letter in some Slavic languages. It is a digraph made of the Latin letters N and J. Nj is used for the sound //. It is the 20th letter of Gaj's Latin alphabet, coming after N and before O.
